<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Page non trouvée - Energreen</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@700&family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<style>
    body {
        background-color: #f0f4f1;
        font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        color: #1a361c;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 50px;
    }
    .error-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background: white;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-top: 5px solid #1a361c;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
        color: #1a361c;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: #493315;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .btn-back, .btn-dashboard {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        margin: 0 10px;
    }
    .btn-back {
        background-color: #6c757d;
        color: white;
    }
    .btn-back:hover {
        background-color: #5a6268;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .btn-dashboard {
        background-color: #1a361c;
        color: white;
    }
    .btn-dashboard:hover {
        background-color: #142a15;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
</style>
<div class="error-container">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <h2>Page non trouvée</h2>
    <p>Désolé, la page que vous recherchez n'existe pas ou a été déplacée.</p>
    <button onclick="goBack()" class="btn-back" style="border: none; cursor: pointer;">Retour à la page précédente</button>
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-dashboard">Aller au tableau de bord</a>
    <a href="/login" class="btn-back" style="margin-top: 10px; display: block;">Aller à la page de connexion</a>
</div>
<script>
    function goBack() {
        if (window.history.length > 1) {
            window.history.back();
        } else {
            window.location.href = '/dashboard';
        }
    }
</script>
</body>
</html>
